<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(خم)</span> ,<span class="c5"> وَعَنْ مُجَاهِدٍ قَالَ:</span> لَا يَتَعَلَّمُ الْعِلْمَ مُسْتَحْيٍ وَلَا مُسْتَكْبِرٌ. <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
